    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Agree with @JanPetr and not sure why this is implemented like this. The documentation also mentions that the filtering is a number, no specifics that it has to be an integer.\r\n\r\nRight now the only workaround is using a field with an integer number for the filter while having a decimal one for showing the decimal value in the hits. \r\n\r\nI really think is a major issue as it defies the purpose having this filter.",
