    "body": "Cannot judge impact in changing this, but my assumption is that the vast majority has implemented this widget assuming that decimal numbers are handled and they are actually getting the wrong results when they use the star rating widget... in that sense I think it's a major issue, as I think people do not realize that.\r\n\r\nUpdating the documentation would at least help new implementations. \r\n\r\n",
